g>保存注意事项</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">常温下干燥.阴凉处</span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>', 'images/201204/thumb_img/1105_P_1334336316059.jpg', 'images/201204/goods_img/1105_P_1334336316059.jpg', 'images/201204/source_img/1105_P_1334336316059.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1334336315', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1334388085', '1', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '');
