過開水後備用。2. 將油鍋放入薑末、蒜末爆香，沿鍋邊熗酒，隨即下廣達香肉醬，然後放入豆腐和水燒開，轉小火燜煮3分鐘。3. 淋上太粉水勾芡，並灑上蔥末即可。 </span></span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">备注： 素食者可將廣達香肉醬1罐改用廣香吉丁醬2罐去掉蒜末。蔥改成海苔碎片即可。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> <strong>（二）三杯雪螺 </strong><strong>：</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 1. 廣達香肉醬1罐</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. 雪螺肉半斤</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. 薑1小塊、蒜頭5個</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. 紅辣椒2條</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 5. 九層塔嫩葉半杯(約20克)</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 6. 三杯鍋1個燒熱備用 </span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><strong>調味料：</strong> 1. 醬油膏1大匙2. 黑麻油1大匙</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> <strong>作　法</strong><strong>：</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 1. 九層塔嫩葉洗淨，將薑、紅辣椒、蒜頭切片炸金黃色備用。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. 用黑麻油起油鍋爆香薑、紅辣椒、蒜，加入醬油膏與材料1炒至水乾後，再加入九層塔於三杯鍋內即可。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> <span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><strong>肉酱蒸鱼材料：</strong></span><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 1. 廣達香肉醬1罐</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. 尼羅紅魚1條(約1斤</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">)</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 3. 嫩豆腐1盒</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 4. 蔥2枝切末 <br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> <strong>作　法</strong><strong>：</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 1. 將尼羅紅魚洗淨用刀劃成網狀。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 2. 蔥切末，取盤一個將魚擺好，另將廣達香肉醬攪拌淋於魚上面，用猛火蒸約10分鐘後灑上蔥末，淋上熱油即可。</span> \n</p>\n<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><strong>保存注意事项</strong></span> \n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"> 常温下干燥.阴凉处</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>', 'images/201204/thumb_img/1093_P_1334336283703.jpg', 'images/201204/goods_img/1093_P_1334336283703.jpg', 'images/201204/source_img/1093_P_1334336283703.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1334336282', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1336523978', '1', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '');
