ine-height:2.5;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong>食用方法</strong></span></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2.5;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 烧饭、煮八宝粥、制作粘豆包、包粽子等 <br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:16px;color:#000000;\"><strong>保存注意事项</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2.5;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 常温下干燥.阴凉处</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>', 'images/201204/thumb_img/1115_1335488051711.jpg', 'images/201204/goods_img/1115_1335488051711.jpg', 'images/201204/source_img/1115_1335488051711.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1334336341', '57', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1338760608', '1', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '');
