的作用。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;\"> 4、 奶酪中含量丰富的锌有助于儿童的智力发育。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>', 'images/201204/thumb_img/1163_P_1334336653263.jpg', 'images/201204/goods_img/1163_P_1334336653263.jpg', 'images/201204/source_img/1163_P_1334336653263.jpg', '1', '', '0', '1', '0', '0', '1334336652', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1336523958', '1', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '');
