;\">等多种维生素</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\">。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>', 'images/201204/thumb_img/1514_P_1334338470104.jpg', 'images/201204/goods_img/1514_P_1334338470104.jpg', 'images/201204/source_img/1514_P_1334338470104.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1334338469', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1334388082', '1', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '');
