SimSun;\">芡实、淮山药、薏仁</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:large;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">【规</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;\">格】</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">400克（内分小包装）</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">【食用方法】</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">：</span><span style=\"font-size:medium;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\"><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">1.取本品一包用开水边冲边搅拌至糊状即可食用（微波炉转下更好），可以根据口味适当加些糖。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">2.取本品一包，少许温水调成很稠的糊状，然后开水边冲调边搅拌，充分溶解后饮用。</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"layout-grid-mode:char;text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#000000;font-family:SimSun;\">（本品为原生态制品，未添加任何调味料，为原质。气味感稍差，消费者可以根据个人口味，加糖，加蜂蜜，加咸料饮用。）</span> \n</p>\n<br />', 'images/201204/thumb_img/1545_P_1334338638514.jpg', 'images/201204/goods_img/1545_P_1334338638514.jpg', 'images/201204/source_img/1545_P_1334338638514.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1334338637', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1334388082', '1', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '0', '');
