ize:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun,arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;line-height:2;\">内包装：真空小袋</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:12px/18px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#888888;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun,arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<h2 style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;font-size:14px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;line-height:20px;padding-top:0px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;border-right-width:0px;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:22px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun,arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;\">端午节吃粽子的由来|为什么端午节吃粽子</span></span></span></span></span> \n	</h2>\n	<h2 style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;font-size:14px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;line-height:20px;padding-top:0px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:center;border-right-width:0px;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\">&nbsp;</span></span> \n	</h2>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">在很久很久以前，赵家浜有个赵土根，给地主做长工，一家老小五口难以养活，他听说跑码头能多赚些钱，于是就跟着人去了码头。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">赵土根一去就是三年，没有音信。妻子赵氏在家里带着孩子抚养老人，挖野菜、做零工，勉强度日。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun,arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;\">然而，有一天，年迈的婆婆却病倒了。老人家一连几日茶饭不思，清醒的时候看着饭菜说不饿，而在神志不清的时候却叨咕着要吃粽子。这一家子日常生活都十分艰难，哪有余钱买米裹粽子。媳妇赵氏除了偷偷抹泪，就是每天天刚蒙蒙亮去一座破庙里，给婆婆祈祷。</span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">端午节这天早上，赵氏从庙里回来，正在路上走着，突然有一条黑狗向她吠叫着扑了过来，赵氏连忙躲闪，不小心绊倒了，那狗见赵氏摔倒在路边草丛中，抖了抖毛摇摇尾巴。这时候，赵氏看到有许多米粒从狗身上掉下来，可不知为什么，那狗在地上的米粒上来回踏了三圈，然后摇摇尾巴远去了。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">赵氏待到那狗离开后，才站起来，走近一看，看见地上的米粒竟然是糯米。她的眼睛一亮，伸手就要去捡那米粒，又迟疑地停住了手，毕竟那米粒是从狗身上掉下来的，何况又被狗踩踏了那么多次。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun,arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;\">赵氏没有捡米粒就往回走，可是走了几步她又停下了，反反复复来去了好几回，最后她还是一粒一粒地把米粒捡起来，拿回了家里。</span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">回到家后，赵氏一个人悄悄地反复地冲洗那把米，糯米非常洁净了，然而赵氏还是觉得不干净。赵氏把淘洗好的糯米一口一口用嘴含了一遍，然后又继续清洗。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">时近中午，赵氏把亮晶晶的糯米用芦苇叶子包成了两个粽子，煮熟后剥好端到婆婆的床前，昏睡的婆婆闻到粽子的香味睁开了眼睛。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun,arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;\">赵氏喂婆婆吃好粽子，不一会的时间，婆婆坐了起来，精神非常好。赵氏却有些害怕，怕婆婆是回光返照。</span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">就在这个时候，晴朗的天突然雷声大作，一个个炸雷围着茅草房炸个不停。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">赵氏的脸顿时变得煞白，扑通一声跪倒在婆婆床前哭着说：“婆婆，对不起！儿媳再不能伺候您了，这雷公是来抓我的。”</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">婆婆见状，急忙下床搀扶儿媳起来说：“快别瞎说，雷公怎么会抓你这么贤惠又孝道的人呢，快起来！”</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">赵氏的三个孩子也吓得大哭起来。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">赵氏哭着把粽子的来历向婆婆说了，婆婆听后非常感动，跪在地上对着屋外哀求着说：“雷公爷爷，我的媳妇非常孝敬老人，您千万别抓她走啊！”</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">雷声还是不停，而且一声比一声响，大地都颤抖了。这时婆婆哭着说：“雷公爷爷，您一定要劈，就劈掉我儿媳一只手吧！”</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">说 着，老人攥住儿媳的胳膊，把赵氏的一只手从窗口伸到了外面。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">一个响雷刚过，婆婆赶紧拉回赵氏的胳膊。赵氏只觉得手心刷地一凉，以为是手被雷劈掉了。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">就在婆婆拉回赵氏的同时，一团黑乎乎的东西也随之进了屋子，天空顿时又晴朗了起来。&nbsp; </span><br />\n</span></span></span></span></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">婆婆发现赵氏的手掌没有劈掉，只是她的手攥成了拳头伸不开。婆婆哭着帮赵氏把手掰开，过了好一阵子，赵氏的拳头终于掰开了，只见她的手中有一只金灿灿的元宝。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">这时，赵氏的三个孩子惊叫起来：“娘、奶奶，我们有很多的粽子！”</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">婆婆与赵氏一看，地上果真有一大袋粽子。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">赵氏一家每人吃了只粽子，然后把剩下的粽子分给了左邻右舍的穷苦人家。说来也怪，赵氏的三个骨瘦如柴的孩子，吃了粽子后，身体强壮了很多，有好几个正在生病的人吃了这粽子，竟然都神奇地痊愈了。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:14px/20px simsun, arial;text-transform:none;color:#444444;text-indent:0px;padding-top:0px;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;border-right-width:0px;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;border-image:initial;\">\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"display:inline! important;font-weight:normal;float:none;word-spacing:0px;text-transform:none;text-indent:0px;line-height:18px;font-style:normal;font-family:simsun, arial;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:normal;background-color:#ffffff;text-align:left;font-variant:normal;widows:2;orphans:2;webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">乡亲们都认为，端午节这天吃粽子可以强身健体还能治病，因此，每年的端午节，人们都要包上几个粽子吃。就这样，渐渐形成了一个端午吃粽子的习俗，一直延续到今天。</span></span></span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"font-size:24px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:幼圆;\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"border-top-width:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-left:0px;border-left-width:0px;border-bottom-width:0px;padding-bottom:0px;margin:0px;word-spacing:0px;font:12px/18px simsun, arial;t